data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath townhouse that includes an ally garage with a separate tax ID: 0328058125 001, nestled on Frederick Avenue in the heart of Baltimore, Maryland. This well-maintained property offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and historic charm, making it an ideal home for those seeking a convenient urban lifestyle.   As you enter, you are greeted by a warm and inviting living space, adorned with hardwood floors and ample natural light that fills the room. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living area to the dining space, creating a perfect environment for entertaining friends and family.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring contemporary appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient layout that enhances functionality. Whether you're preparing daily meals or hosting gatherings, this kitchen is both stylish and practical.  Upstairs, you'll find three well-appointed bedrooms, each offering a tranquil retreat with comfortable spaces and generous closet storage. The full bathroom is tastefully designed, providing a relaxing oasis with modern fixtures and finishes.  The townhouse also boasts a convenient half-bath on the main level, adding an extra layer of comfort and functionality to daily living. Additionally, the property includes a private backyard or patio space, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities or simply unwinding after a busy day.  Situated on Frederick Avenue, this townhouse is centrally located, offering easy access to a variety of local amenities, shopping centers, dining options, and cultural attractions. Commuting is a breeze with nearby public transportation options and major roadways in close proximity.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhouse on Frederick Avenue your home. Experience the best of Baltimore living with a perfect blend of historic charm and modern convenience. Schedule a viewing today and envision the lifestyle that awaits in this delightful urban retreat.
